This is a stock bug that has been around since .23 . There is no fix , but you can make your docking ports a decoupler (code below). Just make sure when you decouple (un-dock) that you do it from the ejecting vessel as the docking port will be disposed of. ALso get Kerbal Attachment System and make all docking ports grabbable. This way you can install docking ports in mid-flight.

    MODULE{ name = ModuleDecouple ejectionForce = 5 explosiveNodeID = top}

